headline: Autodesk BioDapt Alliance Highlights AI Role In Real World Prosthetics
summary: Autodesk and BioDapt have partnered to develop next generation prosthetics for para athletes using Autodesk Fusion's AI powered design and manufacturing tools. The collaboration focuses on scaling high performance assistive devices that can be tailored to individual athletes and potentially broader patient groups. The partnership highlights a real world use case for Autodesk's AI driven engineering capabilities beyond traditional design and manufacturing. For investors watching...
